{"id":958,"date":"2024-06-28T19:55:52","date_gmt":"2024-06-28T19:55:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/?p=958"},"modified":"2024-06-28T19:58:38","modified_gmt":"2024-06-28T19:58:38","slug":"verschillende-goederen-donaties-aan-de-pupillen-van-prasoro","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/2024\/06\/28\/verschillende-goederen-donaties-aan-de-pupillen-van-prasoro\/","title":{"rendered":"Verschillende goederen donaties aan de pupillen van Prasoro"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>In de maand juni hebben onze pupillen van verschillende families binnen en buiten Suriname donaties in goederen mogen ontvangen. Het gaat hierbij om onder andere kleding en ondergoed, slippers, tandenborstels, tandpasta en zwemkleding. Bijgaand wat beeldmateriaal met een deel van de goederen. Onze dank aan deze families die onze kinderen een warm hart toedragen en gul geven aan onze kids.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-960\" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Jeansbroeken-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Jeansbroeken-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Jeansbroeken-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/>\u00a0 \u00a0<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-959\" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Zwemkleding-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Zwemkleding-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Zwemkleding-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/>\u00a0 <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-961\" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Kids-met-hun-jeansbroek-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Kids-met-hun-jeansbroek-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Kids-met-hun-jeansbroek-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In de maand juni hebben onze pupillen van verschillende families binnen en buiten Suriname donaties in goederen mogen ontvangen. Het gaat hierbij om onder andere kleding en ondergoed, slippers, tandenborstels, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-958","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-uncategorized"],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/958","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=958"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/958\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":973,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/958\/revisions\/973"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=958"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichting